aliases: きまぐれオレンジロード
description:
Proper Japanese Title: きまぐれオレンジロード

Originally serialized in Weekly Shonen Jump, Kimagure Orange Road is notable for the fact that despite being a romantic comedy (with its own twist) in a magazine filled with battle shonen such as Dragon Ball and Hokuto no Ken it was actually one of the most popular titles in the early years of the Golden Age of Jump.
name: Kimagure Orange Road
